These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, milk, water, soy-milk, tea
6 different pets are kept: ferret, turtle, dog, fish, rabbit, chinchilla
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 2. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 5. the owner of the dog is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 7. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1
 8. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
 9. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person drinking milk is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
11. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
12. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |    3     |  4   |       5       |   6   |
| Beverage   | water | tea | coffee    | 7up | milk | soy-milk |
| Pet        | turtle      | chinchilla  | fish | ferret | rabbit          | dog  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, iced-tea, fanta, water, sprite, 7up
There are 6 different nationalities: mexican, german, spanish, australian, indonesian, polish
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 2. the mexican is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 3. the australian is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 4. the australian is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 5. the indonesian is on the far right##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is the spanish##1
 7. the person drinking water is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 8. the polish is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1
10. the australian is on the right of the spanish##1
11. the indonesian is on the left or right of the german##3
12. the german is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
13. the spanish is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
14. the spanish is on the left or right of the mexican##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |       3       |    4     |     5     |    6     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk  | water     | iced-tea | fanta    | 7up       | sprite  |
| Nationality   | polish | mexican | spanish       | australian | german | indonesian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-3::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  social-worker, firefighter, designer, police-officer, bartender, software-developer
The people use 6 different means of transport: trike, subway, boat, car, ship, tram
1. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
2. the bartender is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
3. the social-worker is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
4. the designer is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
5. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
6. the police-officer is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
7. the firefighter is between the police-officer and the designer##2
8. the bartender is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |      3      |     4     |    5     |     6     |
| Job         | police-officer | firefighter | designer | bartender | social-worker  | software-developer    |
| Transport   | tram      | boat  | ship  | subway       | trike | car |

