.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-4::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, sprite, milk, mirinda, coffee
The people have 6 different hobbies: filmmaking, rock-climbing, cooking, board-games, collecting, dancing
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 8. the person drinking coffee is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person drinking mirinda##2
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
10. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5    |       6       |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | coffee     | mirinda | water        | milk   | sprite |
| Hobby      | filmmaking | collecting | cooking  | rock-climbing | dancing | board-games       |

