.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-5::.
There 6 different types of food: potato, onion, eggplant, peas, grapes, garlic
There are 6 different nationalities: dutch, colombian, italian, australian, british, french
1. the person eating eggplant is between the person eating potato and the person eating grapes##2
2. the french is on the left or right of the italian##3
3. the british is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
4. the french is the person eating onion##1
5. the italian is on the far right##1
6. the dutch is the person eating grapes##1
7. the person eating peas is on the far right##1
8. the british is on the far left##1
9. the dutch is on the left of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |     5     |    6     |
| Food          | garlic | grapes | eggplant | potato | onion | peas   |
| Nationality   | british   | dutch   | colombian    | australian | french    | italian |

