.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-6::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  architect, social-worker, chef, engineer, dressmaker, electrician
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: weightlifting, biathlon, rowing, rugby, tennis, sailing
 1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the architect##3
 2. the architect is between the person who's sport is rugby and the electrician##2
 3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the chef##1
 5. the engineer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 6. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
 7. the architect is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 8. the engineer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 9. the electrician is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
10. the social-worker is on the far left##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |   2    |     3     |     4      |      5       |        6        |
| Job     | social-worker        | engineer | electrician | architect  | chef  | dressmaker |
| Sport   | rowing | biathlon   | weightlifting  | sailing | rugby | tennis          |

