.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-8::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, sprite, coffee, almond-milk, soy-milk
The people have 6 different hobbies: card-games, hiking, camping, fishing, filmmaking, board-games
 1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person drinking sprite##1
 2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
 8. the person drinking milk is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 9. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person drinking soy-milk##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2     |   3   |    4     |    5    |     6      |
| Beverage   | milk | soy-milk     | coffee | sprite | fanta    | almond-milk        |
| Hobby      | camping   | fishing | card-games | filmmaking   | board-games | hiking |

