 1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the nigerian##1
 2. the nigerian is the owner of the horse##1
 3. the egyptian is on the left of the turkish##1
 4. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the argentine##3
 5. the owner of the snake is the egyptian##1
 6. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the argentine##3
 7. the mexican is the owner of the dog##1
 8. the mexican is on the right of the turkish##1
 9. the egyptian is between the turkish and the owner of the horse##2
10. the owner of the frog is the argentine##1
11. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the polish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |    5     |     6     |
| Nationality   | polish | argentine | nigerian | egyptian   | turkish | mexican |
| Pet           | rat    | frog    | horse   | snake | turtle | dog      |

