.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-10::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: tea, iced-tea, cola, milk, water, coffee
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: ice-hockey, cycling, soccer, lacrosse, volleyball, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
9. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person drinking cola and the person who's sport is soccer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |    3    |    4     |      5      |       6       |
| Beverage   | coffee  | water | tea     | milk    | iced-tea | cola |
| Sport      | ice-hockey | volleyball   | lacrosse | soccer | cycling    | swimming       |

