.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-11::.
There 6 different types of food: lettuce, grapes, grapefruit, zucchini, broccoli, orange
6 different pets are kept: rabbit, hedgehog, fish, hamster, goat, frog
 1. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 2. the owner of the goat is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 4. the person eating lettuce is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 6. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
 7. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
 8. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
10. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
11. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |   2   |   3    |   4    |      5      |     6     |
| Food   | lettuce | grapefruit | orange | zucchini | broccoli | grapes |
| Pet    | fish     | hamster | frog | hedgehog | rabbit         | goat       |

