.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-12::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, cola, sprite, lemonade, mirinda, milk
There 6 different types of food: cherry, plum, cucumber, lemon, spinach, cabbage
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
2. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
5. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the person eating spinach##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
8. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |      3      |   4    |     5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | sprite  | milk      | iced-tea | mirinda  | cola    | lemonade |
| Food       | spinach | cabbage | cucumber        | cherry | lemon | plum        |

