There are 6 different nationalities: canadian, american, japanese, brazilian, italian, indonesian
 1. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 2. the fan of soul is the indonesian##1
 3. the fan of funk is on the right of the japanese##1
 4. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
 5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 6. the fan of blues is on the left of the american##1
 7. the canadian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
 8. the american is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
 9. the fan of hip-hop is the japanese##1
10. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
11. the fan of r&b is the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2   |     3      |    4    |    5     |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | soul | hip-hop   | funk     | r&b    | blues     | jazz |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | japanese | canadian | italian | brazilian | american   |

