The people use 6 different means of transport: ship, boat, snowmobile, skateboard, tram, scooter
 1. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person eating peas##3
 3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3
 5. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person eating pear is between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the boat##2
 8. the person driving the ship is the person eating pomegranate##1
