10. the person eating peas is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |    3     |     4     |     5      |   6    |
| Food        | peas  | pear | cranberry | grapes | pomegranate   | corn |
| Transport   | boat | snowmobile | skateboard    | tram     | ship | scooter    |

