 4. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 5. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the person eating kale is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking tea##2
 8. the person eating asparagus is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
10. the person eating kale is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
