.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: writing, sudoku, gardening, chess, drawing, traveling
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, water-polo, snowboarding, lacrosse, badminton
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
 2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |    5    |      6      |
| Hobby   | writing | gardening | chess | drawing     | sudoku | traveling |
| Sport   | ice-hockey    | snowboarding  | water-polo   | baseball | lacrosse   | badminton    |

 